@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Listar todos los vehículos
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehiculos
Accept: application/json

### 2. Obtener vehículo por ID (usa la variable compartida vehiculoId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehiculos/{{vehiculoId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Verificar vehículo creado
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehiculos/{{vehiculoId}}
Accept: application/json